{
  "stem": "1603.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how I found out that he died.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was in 1945, early 1945.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we were liberated in January 1945, and so that was after the liberation or so.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so I never going to forget Robbie, my friend.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I hope he's listening to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] many, many people in the school I, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was an interesting thing also, an experience that-- because there was not enough room.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to switch.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So there were girls separately and boys going separately in the same classes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But let's say the boys would be going from 8:00 in the morning till noon, and the girls would come at 12:30 and be till 4:00.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one day-- one day, I left my book in-- in-- in my place where I was sitting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my name was written in it, Peter Fischl.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so the a girl who sat in the same place knew who sits there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she carved in, heaven knows why, she carved in this wooden [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] chair in the writing arrangement-- I don't know if you're familiar with it, old European school system where you sit and then here is where you write.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And everything is made out of wood.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And she carved in that-- she carved in a heart and she said-- she wrote in-- carved in, 'I love you, Peter.' And, and till this day, I'm thinking who Renee could have been.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And many times, I'm thinking was-- that I should have maybe made a harder effort to search for her, which I did not.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's kind of the mystery woman in my life and the mystery person in my life.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, probably 12 or 13.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
